originalText.text:
Elaine is great!

She cares about her students and has a very warm philosophy to teaching. It doesn't matter what your background is, what your experience level is, what genre of singing you're interested in - Elaine can help!

I've been taking singing lessons with her for over a year now and have noticed significant improvement in my sound!

originalText.text: Elaine is the best! A year ago I walked into her studio overcome with shyness and convinced that I'd never feel excited or confident about singing around others. Today I can say I feel completely differently (for the better) thanks to her. She gave me the tools to level up my singing significantly. She is also an excellent motivator, always keeping an eye on my progress and reminding me of how far I've come while pushing me to keep building and refining new skills. I recommend her every chance I get!

originalText.text: Elaine Romanelli is an absolutely FANTASTIC voice teacher.  My singing improved immediately after only one lesson! and in very short order I am sounding way better than I ever dreamed I could sound, and feeling way more comfortable in my voice than I ever have.  Elaine is incredibly skilled and knowledgeable, very positive, always clear and always kind.  Five stars doesn't even begin to do her justice.   Thank you Elaine for giving me my voice back!!!!!
